  "texts": [
    "In this study, we present a sociological personality analysis that integrates hypergraphs with LLMs in online social networks.",
    "We offer a very useful dataset to support such thorough analysis.",
    "We effectively combine fragmented user data with complex social environments into comprehensive user understanding.",
    "Our experimental results demonstrate that this method significantly improves the performance of personality analysis, providing deeper insights into user interactions and their social environments.",
    "This work highlights the potential of hypergraph-based models to advance sociological analysis and enrich our understanding of human behavior in digital environments."
